					<article id="post-1657597" class="post-1657597 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-business tag-top-stories border-top clearfix has-thumbnail">
				<span class="channel-label business-post"><a href="http://venturebeat.com/category/business/">Business</a></span>								<div class="entry-wrapper">
					<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title">Why investors still love Twitter: a guide for the rest of&nbsp;us</h1>
												<div class="entry-content-thumbnail">
							<img  src="//vbstatic.co/assets/img/logo-placeholder.png" data-src="http://i1.wp.com/venturebeat.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/9359575577_380684839f_k.jpg?fit=780%2C9999" class="attachment-single wp-post-image" alt="Twitter buttons" /><noscript><img src="http://i1.wp.com/venturebeat.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/9359575577_380684839f_k.jpg?fit=780%2C9999" class="attachment-single wp-post-image" alt="Twitter buttons" /></noscript><div class="wp-caption"><div class="vb_image_source"><em>Image Credit: <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/garrettheath/9359575577/in/photolist-fg5gJH-6Nuj9w-6Lb4yf-5Qax2c-5ro1T9-5qtbaW-6Bxfdw-7aXhjJ-7U4KnJ-65Hcmv-bKUVDn-8nAByF-6NM2tt-4qVUMu-6yNCXa-a1vp4W-8oTdWZ-ayDr8X-3McFgH-7FutAY-6aKyLM-cAT173-5JUo43-aDHpGW-6XoNHZ-7tygge-a1swhv-9aHWfJ-5XW7XZ-f9G133-5dwffj-e1GtBw-5Bi2KA-5BpnGU-cp4fTm-f7syrv-7heFbz-xhWkS-5Weiy6-6986AJ-artgBQ-eRooBr-7SGo1D-7i765k-4qCtaS-692uaB-4CHZgS-avx5pY-7yuDYM-CFpbM" target="_blank">Garrett Heath</a></em></div></div>						</div><!-- .entry-content-thumbnail -->
						
						<div class="entry-meta clearfix">
							<div class="entry-meta-left">
								<time class="the-time" title="2015-02-08T13:48:17+00:00" datetime="2015-02-08T13:48:17+00:00">February 8, 2015 1:48 PM</time><br/>
								<a href="http://venturebeat.com/author/harrison-weber/" title="Posts by Harrison Weber" class="author url fn" rel="author">Harrison Weber</a>							</div><!-- .entry-meta-left -->
							<div class="entry-meta-right">
											<div class="vb-social-share sharrre_widget">
